summary: Mankey truffles made out of extra cake bits and cream cheese frosting, inspired by the current fighting-type event in Pokemon...
body:
Mankey truffles made out of extra cake bits and cream cheese frosting, inspired by the current fighting-type event in Pokemon Go.

They look angry, maybe it was a bad idea to bite one of them?! Mankey no doubt fight dirty even in chocolate form, I hope they don’t know Revenge 🙊💢
